✅ 1. EVEN NUMBER OF 0’s
✔ Regular Expression:
(1*01*01*)*
________________________________________
🔧 Steps in JFLAP (Manual DFA – BEST)
1.	Open JFLAP 
2.	Click → Finite Automaton 
🔹 Create States
•	q0 (even 0’s) 
•	q1 (odd 0’s) 
🔹 Set:
•	q0 → Initial + Final 
🔹 Add Transitions
q0 --0--> q1
q1 --0--> q0
q0 --1--> q0
q1 --1--> q1
________________________________________
🧠 Logic
•	0 toggles state 
•	1 does nothing 
________________________________________
✅ 2. STRING CONTAINING “ABA”
✔ Regular Expression:
(A|B)*ABA(A|B)*
________________________________________
🔧 Steps in JFLAP
🔹 Create States
•	q0 → initial 
•	q1 → seen A 
•	q2 → seen AB 
•	q3 → seen ABA (final) 
________________________________________
🔹 Transitions
q0 --A--> q1
q0 --B--> q0

q1 --A--> q1
q1 --B--> q2

q2 --A--> q3
q2 --B--> q0

q3 --A--> q3
q3 --B--> q3
________________________________________
🧠 Logic
•	Track sequence A → AB → ABA 
•	Once found → stay in final state 
________________________________________
✅ 3. STARTS WITH “A” AND ENDS WITH “B”
✔ Regular Expression:
A(A|B)*B
________________________________________
🔧 Steps in JFLAP
🔹 Create States
•	q0 → start 
•	q1 → valid started with A 
•	q2 → last symbol is A 
•	q3 → last symbol is B (FINAL if valid) 
•	qd → dead state
________________________________________
🔹 Transitions
q0 --A--> q1
q0 --B--> qd

q1 --A--> q2
q1 --B--> q3

q2 --A--> q2
q2 --B--> q3

q3 --A--> q2
q3 --B--> q3

qd --A--> qd
qd --B--> qd________________________________________
⚠️ Add DEAD state
•	For invalid start (if starts with B) 
•	Add new state → right click → set name “qd” or “qdead”.
________________________________________
✅ 4. STARTS WITH “AA” AND ENDS WITH “BB”
✔ Regular Expression:
AA(A|B)*BB
________________________________________
🔧 Steps in JFLAP
🔹 Create States
•	q0 → start 
•	q1 → seen first A 
•	q2 → seen AA (valid start done) 
•	q3 → middle (any A/B) 
•	q4 → last symbol B 
•	q5 → last two symbols BB (FINAL) 
•	qd → dead state________________________________________
🔹 Transitions
q0 --A--> q1
q0 --B--> qd

q1 --A--> q2
q1 --B--> qd

q2 --A--> q2
q2 --B--> q3

q3 --A--> q2
q3 --B--> q4

q4 --A--> q2
q4 --B--> q5

q5 --A--> q2
q5 --B--> q5

qd --A--> qd
qd --B--> qd________________________________________
⚠️ Important
•	Must ensure ends with BB 
•	So final state only when last two inputs are B 


