Click State Creator Tool (circle icon)
Create 2 states:
•	q0 
•	q1 
________________________________________
🔹 Step 2: Set Start State
👉 Right click on q0
→ Click Initial
________________________________________
🔹 Step 3: Set Final State
👉 Right click on q0
→ Click Final
✔ Because:
•	Even number of 0’s includes 0, 2, 4... 
•	So start state is also accepting 
________________________________________
🔹 Step 4: Add Transitions
Click Transition Tool (arrow icon)
Add transitions:
1.	q0 → q1 with input: 0
2.	q1 → q0 with input: 0
3.	q0 → q0 with input: 1
4.	q1 → q1 with input: 1
________________________________________
🧠 Logic
State	Meaning
q0	Even 0’s
q1	Odd 0’s
